                            <comment id="105024" author="snicoll" created="Fri, 27 Jun 2014 11:20:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;And &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-boot/issues/1182&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;#1182&lt;/a&gt; is the related issue in Boot to make that transparent.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
